            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Hd1e108">Rubrica 12</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De humana consolatione miserorum</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e114">
      <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>¶ De humana consolatione mi
      <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>serorum. Rubrica. 12.
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e121">
      <lb ed="#V" n="62"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e118">IOB. Hystoria. capitulo 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e120">Quidam ami
      <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>cus iob nomine elipham: con
      <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>solatus fuit iob in aduersitatibus su
      <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>is his verbis: Docuisti multos: et ma
      <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>nus lapsas roborasti: vacillantes confirmaue
      <lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>runt sermones tui: et genua trementia confor
      <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>tasti. Nunc autem venit super te plaga: et
      <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>defecisti: tetegit te deus et conturbatus es:
      <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>vbi est timor tuus: fortitudo tua: et perfe
      <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>fectio manuum tuarum: Recordare obse
      <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>cro te quis vnquam inuocens periit: aut quae
      <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>do recti deleti sunt: quinpotius vidi eos quie
      <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>operantur iniquitatem et seminant dolores
      <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>et metunt eos flante deo perisse: et spiritu ire
      <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>eius esse consumptos.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e156">
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e158">Cronica de nugis philosophorum. capitulo 4. scilicet
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>de chilone.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e160">Chilo lacedemonius qui fuit
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>vnus de. vii. sapiententibus iubebat citius ad ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>lamitates amicorum quam ad prosperitates ire.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e171">
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e176">Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiastico. capitulo 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e175">Non desis plorantibus in consolatione.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e181">
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e188">Ouidius de tristibus. libro 5. epistola 9.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e185">Detineo studiis animum: falloque dolores
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>Experior: curis et dare verba meis.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e193">
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e202">Idem <unclear>methamorph</unclear>. libro 15. et finali.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e197">Neque enim fortuna querenda.
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>Sola tua est: similes aliorum respice casus
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>Mitius ista feres: vtinamque exempla dolentem
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>Non mea te possent releuare: sed et mea possunt.</quote> <!--324.xml-->
          <pb ed="#V" n="143-r"/>
          <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e216">
        <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e227">Seneca de tranquillitate animi:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e220">Si te ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>studia reuocaueris: omne vite fastidium effugies</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-d1e226">
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Rd1e239">Idem de consolatione ad paulinum:</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e09200-Qd1e230">Studia
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>optime felicitatem extollunt: et facilime ca
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>lamitatem minuunt.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
